+Debug UART
+^^^^^^^^^^
+
+The Debug UART is provided with the following settings::
+
+    CONFIG_DEBUG_UART=y
+    CONFIG_DEBUG_UART_SIFIVE=y
+    CONFIG_DEBUG_UART_BASE=0x38000000
+    CONFIG_DEBUG_UART_CLOCK=390000000
